Title: An Act Changing the Name of Mababang Paaralan Ng Orani North Annex in Barangay Paraiso, Municipality of Orani, Province of Bataan, to Mababang Paaralan Ng Paraiso
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 209
An Act Changing the Name of Mababang Paaralan Ng Orani North Annex in Barangay Paraiso, Municipality of Orani, Province of Bataan, to Mababang Paaralan Ng Paraiso
Section 1. The name of Mababang Paaralan ng Orani North Annex in Barangay Paraiso, Municipality of Orani, Province of Bataan, is hereby changed to Mababang Paaralan ng Paraiso.
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: March 25, 1982
